    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>How about:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public static final byte[] intToByteArray(int value) {\n    return new byte[] {\n            (byte)(value &gt;&gt;&gt; 24),\n            (byte)(value &gt;&gt;&gt; 16),\n            (byte)(value &gt;&gt;&gt; 8),\n            (byte)value};\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>The idea is <em>not mine</em>. I've taken it from <a href=\"http://snippets.dzone.com/posts/show/93\" rel=\"noreferrer\">some post on dzone.com</a>.</p>\n"
