    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you're using <a href=\"https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-lang/apidocs/org/apache/commons/lang3/Conversion.html#intToByteArray-int-int-byte:A-int-int-\" rel=\"noreferrer\">apache-commons</a></p>\n\n<pre><code>public static byte[] toByteArray(int value) {\n    byte result[] = new byte[4];\n    return Conversion.intToByteArray(value, 0, result, 0, 4);\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 17976446,
      "reputation" : 290,
      "user_id" : 13063887,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/dfae7d9b51c2c140541b690765467e19?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
